      "author": "israerusan",
      "description": "Big update: a redesigned dashboard and a Free/Pro split.\n\n## Free (new polish)\n- **Vault-health gauge** with an A–F letter grade and a one-line verdict\n- **Insights** — your scores turned into a ranked, most-urgent-first to-do list\n- Refined header, summary tiles, hover states, and sticky columns\n\n## Pro ($6 one-time, verified offline)\n- **Full Insights** + **one-click bulk actions** (disable incompatible/abandoned, mute sideloaded)\n- **Export** reports to **Markdown and CSV**\n- **Health trends** — vault score over time with a sparkline and delta\n- **Auto-refresh on open**\n\nEnter a license key under **Settings → FlowKit Pro** to unlock. No account, no server, no telemetry.\n\n**Manual install:** drop `main.js`, `manifest.json`, and `styles.css` into `<vault>/.obsidian/plugins/flowkit-health-dashboard/`.",
